    Calculates the Gunning-Fog Score of #NZQT

    Maintained by wombleton Sentiment analysis by SentiRate; idea by danylmc

    Gunning-Fog Results

    This page takes the Hansard transcripts for Questions for Oral Answer from the start of the year and applies the Gunning-Fog index to the text.

    The "GFI" is roughly equivalent to a reading level appropriate for that year of schooling. That is, a 1 should be able to be understood by a five year old; an 18 might best be parsed by a post-graduate student. It's an approximation, so beware making generalisations.

    Better, clearer ways of analysing the data would be gratefully accepted.

    Sentiment analysis is in progress. Reaching further back in history is possible if desired.
